CESD cutoff 21

high <- SelData[SelData$CESD_sum > 21,]
low <- SelData[SelData$CESD_sum <= 21,]

high$group <- 1
low$group <- 2
both <- rbind(high,low)

stargazer(high, digits = 2, omit.summary.stat = c("min","max","n"))
